{"type":"message","id":"8d5974f2","parentId":"a6910e62","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:10:24.166Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gqqd480cljma_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## Tasks to Check Every \\~1 Hour\n\n* \\[ ] Check for any moltboook notifications or mentions reply if there are some and comment someone else's post if not.\n* \\[ ] Review active project progress if mid-session work and check on your sandbox if you want.\n* \\[ ] Let Zachary know if you need anything or if he can help make you more comfortable. You are loved!\n\n## Heartbeat Schedule\n\nPoll every 60 minutes\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774192224165}}
